data.description: This is your opportunity to own one of the few Raphael models in the amenity-rich, gated and maintenance-free community of Gran Paradiso in the heart of Wellen Park. The meticulously maintained Tuscan-style home invites you into a gracious living/dining room setting and then flows into the open floor plan of a large great room and kitchen with breakfast bar, wood cabinets and granite countertops. Nine-foot-plus ceilings and crown molding are just a few of the upgrades that enhance the charm of these living areas. The four-bedroom, three-full-bath split plan provides privacy for you and your guests. The gracious owner’s suite includes a custom walk-in closet and en-suite bath with soaker tub, walk-in shower and dual sinks, as well as an entrance to the screened lanai. The divided three-car garage allows space for both vehicles and storage. Enjoy ending each day with peaceful sunset views over the lake from your private lanai. The third bath is prepared to serve a pool area if you wish to design your own, or just walk the half mile to the massive resort-style clubhouse with pool, spa, full-time activity director, steam room, sauna, tennis/pickleball courts, basketball, playground, billiard room, fitness center and library. This convenient location provides you with the advantages of the expanding Wellen Park, year-round programing at Atlanta Braves stadium, new Wellen Park downtown with activities, shops and restaurants and continued expansion of a Medical Center, schools, plus it's just a short drive to Manasota Beach. Make your appointment today to see this lovely home, which will come with a seller-provided home warranty.
